+### 2. 💰 Financial Modeling Suite
+**Location**: `awesome-copilot/skills/financial-modeling-suite/`
+
+**Quick Start**:
+```python
+from awesome_copilot.skills.financial_modeling_suite.scripts.dcf_model import (
+    build_dcf_model, 
+    calculate_wacc,
+    DCFAssumptions
+)
+
