+    model="llama3.2",
+    messages=[
+        {"role": "user", "content": f"Use these tools: {tools_prompt}..."}
+    ]
+)
+
+# Parse response to extract tool calls (regex/structured prompt)
+# Then dispatch to MCP server
+```
